{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_08_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚 2話 爆発しちゃいます！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "渚、先方からのシナリオのサンプルは\n確認してくれたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ did you check\nthe sample scenario they sent over?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　私の要望をなるべく取り入れて\nもらっていて……凄く嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! They incorporated my requests into that\nas many as possible… I’m so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0282993953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "声優に挑戦するのも初めてなので\n心配はありますけど、とっても楽しみなんですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This will be my first time trying voice acting‚ so\nI am a little worried‚ but I’m really looking forward to it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5949660619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "最近は寮で生活する琴乃ちゃんを遠目から眺めて\n琴乃ちゃんに声を当てる特訓をしてるんです！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately I’ve been watching Kotono-chan from a distance at the dorm‚\npracticing voicing Kotono-chan!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0949669521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは、意味あるのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-Does that… actually help…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3616336187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "登場人物の感情を想像しながら演技するのも\n声優としての大事なスキルじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Acting while imagining the character's feeling\nis an important skill for a voice actor‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2917921384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと強引な気もするが……ともあれ、ここなら遠慮\nなく声を出せるから、シナリオを実際に読んでみようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be a bit of a stretch… But anyway‚ we can make\nas much noise as we want‚ so let’s try actually reading the scenario.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6000010491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "……よし、これで二人が付き合うところまでは\n読み終わりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay‚ we’ve finished reading up to the part\nwhere they start dating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1179863293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "次はお泊まりシーンですね\nそれじゃあ、行きます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next is the scene where they go on a sleepover date.\nHere we go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.484652996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "「わー、君の部屋、綺麗だね\n……え、今日のために片付けておいた？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Wow~‚ your room is so clean…\n…Did you clean it up for me today?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3846519787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "「そ、そうなんだ……あはは、嬉しいな\n私、好きな人の部屋に入るの初めてなんだ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I-Is that so… Ahaha‚ I’m happy.\nThis is my first time being in the room of someone I like.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9513186454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "「だ、だから、その……緊張してるけど\nからかったりしちゃ……やだよ？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“S-So‚ um… I’m nervous‚ but…\ndon’t tease me‚ okay?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5513186454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "「お、お風呂、貸してくれてありがと\n君と同じシャンプーを使っちゃった、えへへ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Th-Thanks for letting me use your bathroom…\nI used the same shampoo as you‚ ehehe.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3513242403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "「君と同じ匂いがするのって\nなんだか……とっ、ても、ドキドキ」……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Smelling the same as you makes me…\nS-So‚ so… nervous…” …",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7513242403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "……わぁぁぁ～～！！\nむ、無理！　無理です！　これ以上は無理です～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wahhh!!\nN-No way! I can’t! I can’t read any more~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5513196626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ渚！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong‚ Nagisa!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6846601168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "だ、だって、この後はもっともっと大胆なセリフを\n言うんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But‚ after this‚\nthere are lines that are even bolder‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9447279929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "このまま最後まで読んだら……もう、もう……\n恥ずかし過ぎて爆発しちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I keep reading like this… I‚ I…\nI'll be so embarrassed! I’m gonna explode!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1780613262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "いや、でも、これくらいで諦めるのは申し訳ないし……\n……そうだ！　協力してくれませんか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can’t give up now…\n…That’s it! Will you work with me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2780557314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、私が一人で読んでるから恥ずかしく\nなっちゃうんだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it’s because I’m reading this alone\nthat I’m getting embarrassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0113921165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんと読み合わせすればきっと\nゲームの世界に入り込めて平気になるはずです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we practice our lines together‚ {user}-san‚ I’m sure\nI can get into the world of the game and be fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6447508812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういうものなのか……？\n分かった、協力するよ。どのシーンを読むといいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-Is that how it works…?\nOkay‚ I’ll help you. Which scene should we read?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1333765985,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4866.62416439998,
          "startTime": 150.0000007629
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "ここの……主人公が急に大胆に攻めてくる\nシーンをお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This one… where the protagonist suddenly gets bold…\nI want to try that scene!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9981375377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ここだな。「なぁ、泊まりに来たってことは……\n俺達がこれから何をするか、分かってんだろ？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This one? “Hey‚ you came to sleep over…\nYou know what we’re gonna do now‚ right?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0667017938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "……ほっ\n{user}さんが棒読みで助かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Whew.\nThank goodness you read it so flatly‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.5882111867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "こんなドキドキするセリフを、かっこ良く\n耳元で囁かれちゃったりしたら……危なかったです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you whispered such heart-pounding lines in my ear in a cool way…\nThat would have been dangerous!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.4882111867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "か、感想の前に、セリフを読んでくれないか……？\nというか、今からそんな調子で大丈夫なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-Can you please read the lines before you share your thoughts…?\nMore importantly‚ are you going to be okay with this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.1333511671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……確かに、練習でこんなに緊張してたら\n本番で困りますよね。どうしましょう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… You’re right‚ if I get this nervous during practice‚\nI’ll be in trouble for the real recording. What should I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.8266846339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "これはあくまでサンプルの段階だから\n今から方向性を変えても大丈夫だと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is still just a sample‚\nso I think it’s okay to change the direction now.",
        "id": ""
